创建一个炫酷且带有交互式的登录注册页面需要结合HTML、CSS和JavaScript。以下是一个简化的示例，你可以在需要的地方进行扩展和美化。

### 文件结构
- `index.html`
- `styles.css`
- `scripts.js`

### index.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interactive Login & Register Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div id="form-container">
            <div class="form-toggle">
                <button id="login-toggle">登录</button>
                <button id="register-toggle">注册</button>
            </div>
            <form id="login-form" class="form" autocomplete="off">
                <h2>登录</h2>
                <input type="text" placeholder="用户名" required>
                <input type="password" placeholder="密码" required>
                <button type="submit">登录</button>
            </form>
            <form id="register-form" class="form hidden" autocomplete="off">
                <h2>注册</h2>
                <input type="text" placeholder="用户名" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="邮箱" required>
                <input type="password" placeholder="密码" required>
                <button type="submit">注册</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

### styles.css
```css
body, html {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #f8e71c);
}

.container {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    width: 400px;
    overflow: hidden;
}

#form-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

.form-toggle {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.form-toggle button {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: none;
    font-size: 18px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

.form-toggle button:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
}

.form {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
}

.form.show {
    display: flex;
}

.form input {
    width: 90%;
    margin: 10px 0;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.form button {
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background-color: #ff6b6b;
    color: white;
    font-size: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

.form button:hover {
    background-color: #ee5253;
}

.hidden {
    display: none;
}
```

### scripts.js
```javascript
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const loginToggle = document.getElementById('login-toggle');
    const registerToggle = document.getElementById('register-toggle');
    const loginForm = document.getElementById('login-form');
    const registerForm = document.getElementById('register-form');

    loginToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
        loginForm.classList.add('show');
        registerForm.classList.remove('show');
    });

    registerToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
        registerForm.classList.add('show');
        loginForm.classList.remove('show');
    });
});
```

### 说明
- **HTML**：提供两个表单，一个用于登录，一个用于注册。两个按钮切换表单的显示。
- **CSS**：使用简单的Flexbox布局和渐变背景来创建现代的外观。按钮和输入框有悬停效果。
- **JavaScript**：根据按下的按钮来切换表单的可见性。

这个基础的示例可以根据需求进行进一步的改进，比如添加表单验证、动画效果、复杂的样式等等。如果需要添加背景动画或更多交互，你可以借助CSS动画或者引入第三方JavaScript库来实现。

